* Investigate\nData Skew
** What is Skew
***_ Uneven partition sizes
***_ Few tasks much longer
***_ Most resources idle
** Identify in Spark UI
***_ Stage page → Summary Metrics
***_ Compare Max vs 75th percentile
***_ Max >50% above 75th = skew
** Common Causes
***_ Uneven key distribution
***_ All nulls → same partition
***_ Time-based partitioning
** Resolve with AQE
***_ Adaptive Query Execution
***_ Dynamic skew handling
***_ spark.databricks.optimizer\n.adaptive.enabled
** Other Resolutions
***_ Salt skewed keys
***_ Add random component
***_ Broadcast smaller tables
***_ Avoid shuffle-based joins
@endmindmap
